meaning_str.bing:
num. 十
n. 十个人；十元纸币；(早晨或晚上的)十点钟；十岁

十个人；十元纸币；(早晨或晚上的)十点钟；十岁

十；十个（人或物）；十个单位；<口>十元纸币（美元或英镑）；<英口>10英镑票面的钞票；（扑克牌的）十点；表示十的符号；编号为十的东西（人或物）；10分钟；10岁；（扑克牌的）10点；

1.en: "Well, then, " said the judge to the young man, "I order you to pay ten liras to Wilson. "
1.cn: “那么，”法官对年轻人说，“我命令你付给威尔逊十里拉。”

2.en: There could be no doubt of his being a sensible man. Ten minutes were enough to certify that.
2.cn: 他无疑是个聪明人，这在十分钟里便得到了证实。

3.en: Trains from Shanghai may be up to ten minutes late, on account of repairs to the track.
3.cn: 由于修轨，由于修轨，从上海来的火车可能晚十分钟到达.车可能晚十分钟到达。

0.en: Yeah. Run ten blocks, that'll help the smell.

1.en: What time is it now? Ten o'clock. Hurray.
1.cn: 那么现在是几点呢？十点啦。太好了！

2.en: Well, she should, it was taken ten years ago.
2.cn: 一点都没错，那是十年前的照片了。

3.en: Chop-chop, Leonard. We leave in ten minutes.
3.cn: 莱纳德，麻利点，我们十分钟后出发。

4.en: Hello. You were supposed to be here ten minutes ago.
4.cn: 喂，你们十分钟前就应该到了。

5.en: Until ten years from now when you're still single.
5.cn: 等十年后你还是单身狗，你就有兴趣了。

6.en: In the bedrooms of ten-year-old girls, where they belong.
6.cn: 在十岁小姑娘的卧室里，在那儿才对。

7.en: Seven, eight, nine, ten. Ready or not, here I come.
7.cn: 七，八，九，十！你藏好了吗，我要来找你啦。

8.en: 46. Wow. Who's well educated now, Mr. I-forgot-ten-states?
8.cn: 46个州，那个受过良好教育写不出剩下十州州名的人是谁？

9.en: Oh, come on. I'll give you ten free Ralph Lauren shirts. One. No ten. You said ten. You can't take that back.
9.cn: 我会送你十件罗夫罗兰的衬衫。一件，不，十件，你说十件，你不能反悔。

10.en: Come on Rach, you don't have what, ten minutes? I don't have ten minutes.
10.cn: 你连十分钟都没有？我连十分钟都没有。

11.en: How much is the little balloon? Ten dollars. Ten dollars? It's all for good cause.
11.cn: 哦，这个小气球多少钱？十美元。十美元？都是为了做善事的。

12.en: Five for Deadwind Pass. Ten for the Redridge Mountains. Ten more to protect the city.
12.cn: 五个在逆风小径，十个在赤脊山，还要超过十个保证城市的安全。

13.en: Oh you're gonna do that ten times a day? What? It goes ten times a day. What are we feeding this baby? Indian food?
13.cn: 你每天要丢十次吗？什么？宝宝一天可以拉十次？我们得喂她印度食物吗？

14.en: Is everybody ready? Ready. Counting to ten. One, two, three, four, five, six, seven, eight, nine, ten.
14.cn: 大家都准备好了吗？准备好了！从一数到十！一二，三，四，五，六，七，八，九，十！

15.en: Yes? After seven, there is eight, nine, ten. Eight, nine, ten. Very good.
15.cn: 是的。在七之后，是八，九，十。非常好！

16.en: Drearcliff House, remember that one, john? One murder, ten suspects. Ten, yeah. All of them guilty. Sherlock.
16.cn: 德克利夫庄园，记得吗，约翰？一桩谋杀，十名嫌犯。十个，是的。全都有罪。夏洛克。

17.en: There were six guards, so we decided we'd choose ten people each. That's how we did it every month. We'd all choose ten.
17.cn: 一共六个看守，我们决定每人挑十个。每个月我们都是这么干的。每人选十个。

18.en: And each tree has ten to the fourth connections to the trees around it. And there are ten to the twelfth trees on Pandora.
18.cn: 每棵树与周围树的联结达到十的四次方，而潘多拉星上有十的十二次方棵这样的树。

19.en: Does she have fingers? Yes, she has ten fingers and ten toes. Probably. I'll get back to you after I see her in sandals.
19.cn: 她有手指吗？有，她有十根手指以及十根脚趾。应该啦。等我看到她穿凉鞋我再告诉你。
